<center> *Assistant Professor and Director of Goodman Emotion and Resilience Laboratory at the University of South Florida (USF)* </center>

## Bio

Dr. Fallon Goodman is an Assistant Professor at the University of South Florida (USF). Her research examines how people manage their emotions and build resilience. By using smartphone monitoring technologies, Dr. Goodman can examine participants' daily patterns of emotions and coping, particularly those that underelie social anxiety. She is passionate about spreading knowledge about psychological science and increasing accessibility to research.

